</style></div><div data-rid="25967658-e1af-48e8-ba4e-980c16564f45" class="r-1j7cfbs"><div data-rid="1760f6b6-996d-4a4a-978d-9cb52df053d7" class="r-5sbahv"><div data-rid="65d865b1-4fb9-4e1b-8bc9-364958680d25" class="r-r3l0k5"><div data-rid="614ebf35-b5e3-4491-a0f2-ec2d6260f390" class="r-u2c1vh"><div data-rid="782879f0-c53c-4a10-8853-a151b68fc827" class="r-qlew1i"><div data-rid="167810e2-ebfb-4c83-8606-a71621edd87e" class="r-pv5a9e"><div data-rid="c734d1d6-37bb-4062-b26d-b44b23e82306" class="r-1t0kn6c"><div data-rid="380f8bd5-379f-4058-a106-809ff38952b1" class="r-7guohj"><div data-rid="dc36e502-a1c1-4dde-9b4e-a98ff417bc13" class="r-19s4vfv"><div data-rid="083c1819-e319-4e5f-975e-74ef89e4507d" class="r-qcp67s"><div data-rid="14632639-8517-4ec4-b957-4b8e585e0777" class="r-1abdz1i alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h1><strong>5 Reasons Blume is a Must-Have for Hormonal Acne</strong></h1></span></div><div data-rid="ef0c3470-1e73-44f0-8e1c-d4bb2174069f" class="r-52wb48 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Hormonal acne is <strong>stubborn, unpredictable, and frustrating</strong>. Whether it's caused by stress, periods, or imbalanced hormones, it often feels like nothing truly works—until now. <strong>Blume’s Meltdown Oil is specifically designed to fight acne at the source, while being gentle enough for sensitive, breakout-prone skin.</strong> Here’s why it’s the game-changer your skin needs:</p></span></div><picture data-rid="57d76cd1-515b-42b2-b45b-32c956ba2db9" class="r-1usdanj"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/EI6A3928.jpg?v=1751571022&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/EI6A3928.jpg?v=1751571022&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/EI6A3928.jpg?v=1751571022&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/EI6A3928.jpg?v=1751571022" class="r-zrzsnc" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div><div data-rid="204f7be0-1c8e-48d6-928a-19ff10cb373a" class="r-xk7jyx"><div data-rid="aba21216-bdbe-4476-b4a6-c13c278caac8" class="r-18y5fxd"><div data-rid="4a5bb420-7f28-4923-bb4d-97778328b775" class="r-19duf2q alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h3>1. Targets Hormonal Acne at the Root</h3></span></div><div data-rid="6ab30822-e16d-4629-b40a-c1dd753a1f29" class="r-7cdz33 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Hormonal breakouts are different from regular acne—they stem from deep within the skin, triggered by hormone fluctuations that throw oil production and inflammation into overdrive. Whether it’s due to puberty, pregnancy, menopause, getting off birth control, stress, or really, anything else, these breakouts tend to be stubborn, cystic, and hard to treat with traditional acne products.</p><p><br></p><p>Blume’s plant-powered, highly effective formulas are designed to calm inflammation, regulate oil production, and prevent future breakouts before they even reach the surface. By targeting acne at the root—while it's still forming under the skin—you can stop breakouts before they happen instead of constantly treating them after the fact. With just one easy step, you’ll be on your way to clear, balanced skin—without the frustration of constant hormonal flare-ups.</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="5a620f01-1d33-49cd-b6f0-2f2cbdb2c757" class="r-1elr1jo"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/2_dd176fad-2d50-4a84-b48e-68ed6a4e7aea.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/2_dd176fad-2d50-4a84-b48e-68ed6a4e7aea.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/2_dd176fad-2d50-4a84-b48e-68ed6a4e7aea.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/2_dd176fad-2d50-4a84-b48e-68ed6a4e7aea.png?v=1732078664" alt="Side-by-side comparison of skin before and after treatment, showing significant improvement." class="r-1yl7ej0" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="94cb25d5-f02a-4e78-8603-febdb6cc7d68" class="r-n6h1eb"><div data-rid="362042a7-990a-4f77-8d7c-359b5e1ad216" class="r-17oi5yr"><div data-rid="0478acaa-74c9-47da-83ba-b528edd4bdf6" class="r-1cjv3b7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>2. Won’t Mess with Your Skin Barrier</p></span></div><div data-rid="ff63d9ec-dcaf-4b6b-9d2e-6df027814473" class="r-qwb7e3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Most acne treatments strip your skin, leading to dryness, irritation, and even more breakouts (we see you, over-the-counter spot treatments). Harsh ingredients like benzoyl peroxide and alcohol-based toners can disrupt your skin’s natural protective barrier, leaving it red, flaky, and vulnerable to bacteria—which ironically makes acne worse in the long run.</p><p><br></p><p>Blume takes a gentler, smarter approach. It balances acne-fighting ingredients like Black Cumin Seed Oil and Blue Tansy, to combat hormonal breakouts without over-drying or weakening your skin. This means less irritation, faster healing, and a stronger, healthier skin barrier—so your skin can defend itself against future breakouts instead of constantly feeling inflamed and reactive.</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="b09ebd95-dad3-4cab-acb4-cacc27b6c244" class="r-kiu414"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_07_23dd47b9-e075-4fa7-a2f2-1ef581e07448.png?v=1739651522&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_07_23dd47b9-e075-4fa7-a2f2-1ef581e07448.png?v=1739651522&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_07_23dd47b9-e075-4fa7-a2f2-1ef581e07448.png?v=1739651522&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_07_23dd47b9-e075-4fa7-a2f2-1ef581e07448.png?v=1739651522" class="r-a2bhle" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="045b29f2-eb91-4738-9a15-3f1df2896314" class="r-1x8sghg"><div data-rid="90ea647e-2225-4dfb-bb97-6481e6dd2547" class="r-33q21c"><div data-rid="a5914e18-872b-414f-a4d4-e2de3b1fbd77" class="r-a2abuh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>3. Balances Oil Without Over-Drying</p></span></div><div data-rid="1f64c772-8187-4c21-9f2f-3a3e7e7998c9" class="r-9p49uv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>One of the biggest struggles with hormonal acne? Oily yet dry skin at the same time. Your hormones signal your skin to produce more oil, but at the same time, many acne treatments strip away moisture—leaving your skin both greasy and dehydrated. This imbalance can actually trigger even more breakouts as your skin overcompensates by producing even more oil to make up for the dryness.</p><p><br></p><p>Blume’s formulas are designed to restore balance by regulating excess sebum production while maintaining essential hydration. Instead of harsh, drying ingredients that leave your skin feeling tight and irritated, Blume uses lightweight, non-comedogenic hydrators like aloe and hyaluronic acid to keep your skin nourished without clogging pores. The result? A healthy, balanced complexion that’s never too oily or too dry—just clear, calm, and happy.</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="a6139956-423b-4085-b1c9-666bc34ebef0" class="r-wife9q"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/Sephora-MeltdownOil.png?v=1739336356&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/Sephora-Meltdow