25px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/5_406d3b1d-499a-4b45-b120-02b8e0c1461b.png?v=1732078665" alt="Before-and-after acne treatment progress over several months on different individuals." class="r-1vs08p6" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="16192ad3-173b-43a9-8735-dddea224bd02" class="r-1352l21"><div data-rid="457325cc-c01e-4826-a1c7-1f117c720209" class="r-1hq3w2k"><div data-rid="34b2171b-6061-4b1d-b8d9-c3f4676225da" class="r-1r37ac6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Hormonal acne doesn’t just show up as small, surface-level blemishes—it often appears as deep, cystic pimples that are red, swollen, and painful to the touch. These breakouts form underneath the skin, making them difficult to treat and often taking weeks to heal, sometimes leaving behind dark spots or scarring.</p><p><br></p><p>Blume’s acne-fighting ingredients work beneath the surface to reduce inflammation, calm redness, and speed up healing, so those stubborn, painful breakouts don’t have the chance to stick around. Instead of relying on harsh chemicals that can irritate your skin and cause even more breakouts, Blume’s formulas gently but effectively clear congestion and keep future cystic breakouts at bay—without over-drying, stinging, or making things worse.</p></span></div><div data-rid="ac24a6f9-903f-4ca7-86a9-9a99c5a6edf6" class="r-hx0v3p alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>5. Prevents Those Deep, Painful Breakouts</p></span></div></div></div><picture data-rid="123a0eb8-6bb6-497d-b58c-56d3c1e9103a" class="r-js2yt3"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_06_998bf243-f6e2-475d-a90e-ae2ea7047eca.png?v=1739651406&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/s2342145_av_06_998bf243-f6e2-475d-a90e-ae2ea7047eca.png?v=1739651406&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet=